esday, sentenced a 33 year-old sales girl, Tine Joy, to seven months imprisonment for criminal breach of trust and diversion of sales’ proceeds to boy friend. July 18, 2017 In "News" The Police on Wednesday arraigned Istifanus Gabriel of Wuye, in a Wuse Zone 2 Senior Magistrates’ Court Abuja, for alleged cheating. May 24, 2017 In "News" The police on Tuesday arraigned Vitalis Chijionwa of Kuje, Abuja, in a Wuse Zone 2 Chief Magistrates’ Court for cheating and criminal intimidation. July 26, 2016 In "News"